data.description: Welcome home! Built in 2003. This Fabulous 5-bedroom 4-bathroom home is perfectly situated on a quiet street in West Fargo North Dakota. The exterior of the home features stunning curb appeal, 3 car-garage with both air conditioning, and heat! New shingles were installed in 2021, the home has steel siding, beautiful landscaping, and a large private fenced in backyard that includes a pergola, swing set, and a spectacular deck for entertaining guests. Moving into the house, the updates include new flooring through-out, a gorgeous fireplace in the living room with vaulted ceilings, and a stunning kitchen. The main floor includes the master suit, that features a large walk-in closet, a luxury jacuzzi tub, and double sink. Also two additional bedrooms, and the laundry room! Thats not all, the basement has been finished, and your mind will be blown by the amount of entertainment space! Egress windows have been installed adding two additional bedrooms downstairs as well. A bonus room currently being used as workout room, with so much room for possibilities! Not to mention both the furnace and A/C units were replaced just three years ago!Schedule your private showing today!
